data.description: Dreaming about a home on a large lot where you can relax on the porch with a view of beautiful mountains? This updated 3 + 2 with office has just been painted inside and out, features new carpet throughout living areas and bedrooms,  kitchen has new countertops, cooktop, built-in oven, faucet, garbage disposal, and includes a nice eating nook. Living room has large windows, a skylight, high ceilings, and is open to dining room. The large master bath has new flooring, and amenities including vanity, sink, mirrored cabinet, and toilet. Bedrooms are light and bright. Laundry room inside. Large covered font porch has new outdoor carpet, and amazing view of the mountains and Willow Springs Racetrack. Covered carport/back patio. Roof is five years new. Large garage and workshop - oversized ~500 sq. ft. garage features two 40' sea freight containers built into it; newly painted to match the house. The large 2-1/2 acres are completely fenced, allowing you enough space for all your hobbies.
